dt-option.default:
        The default value for the `-init languages.searchPanes.title` paramater is `-type undefined`. When this is not in place the `-init i18n` function will use 'Filters Active - %d' as a default.


        As standard, SearchPanes will set the title to display the number of filters in the style of the following 'Filters Active - %d'. This property allows that message to be configured.





$(document).ready(function() {
    $('#example').DataTable( {
        searchPanes: true,
        language: {
            searchPanes: {
                title:{
                    _: 'Filters Selected - %d',
                    0: 'No Filters Selected',
                    1: 'One Filter Selected',
                }
            }
        }
    });
});
